Australian Standards / Local Knowledge Questions

Australian employers may ask these even for remote staff.

Are you familiar with Australian electrical standards?
What is AS/NZS 3000?
What is the difference between MEN and TN-C-S systems?
How do Australian commercial installations differ from Philippine projects?
Are you familiar with Australian cable sizing methods?
Have you worked with Australian switchboard schedules?
What is an RCD, and where is it required?
What are common Australian conduit types and cable types?
Are you familiar with NBN or Australian communications standards?
What is your understanding of compliance requirements in Australia?

You do not need to be a licensed Australian electrician to estimate remotely, but familiarity with Australian terminology helps a lot.

